# Calamus API

Blog API that handles your blog applications ;D

This is an open source project that can be found here https://github.com/Wyvarn/calamus

## Health [/health]

Checks the health of the application

### Health [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                'status': 'I am OK! :)'
            }

